      • addable

        public boolean addable(Node n)
        Checks whether a given node can be added to the symmetry. Following ISMAGS, a node can be added only if its name is greater (alphabetically) than the greatest name already used (though any other unique sorting would work as well). This assures no permutations will occur.
        Parameters:
        n - The node to be checked
        Returns:
        True if the node can be added, false if it can not.
